CRM Analytics Requirements

Supported Browsers: all browsers supported by Lightning Experience.

Data Manager: Lightning Web Components must be enabled to use all Data Manager features.

Browser Zoom: 100% zoom settings are required for CRM Analytics.

Screen Resolution: minimum 1024 x 768 pixels.

Mobile Devices: iOS 16.0 or later, Android 5 or later.

Technical Requirements:

Optimize implementation by reviewing minimum and recommended technical requirements.
Test end-user experience with the same geographic location, hardware, browser, network settings, and expected concurrent users.
Recommended specifications:
Octane 2.0 score of 30,000 or greater
Network latency of 150 ms or less
Download speed of 3 Mbps or greater
At least 8 GB of RAM, with 3 GB available for Salesforce browser tabs

Minimum requirements:
Octane 2.0 score of 20,000 or greater
Network latency of 200 ms or less
Download speed of 1 Mbps or greater
At least 5 GB of RAM, with 2 GB available for Salesforce browser tabs

Run the Salesforce Performance test to find your Octane 2.0 score, latency, and download speed.
